<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="HappyFlower" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗨！<delay8 />我來告訴你一件好事吧！<delay20 /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你知道<delay20 />表情是什麼嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嘿嘿，<delay20 />表情指的就是開心的時候，<delay8 />
身體會不自覺出現的反應！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我說的沒錯吧？<delay20 />
是不是能夠<delay8 />更強烈地表達出情緒啊？<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />當你想做表情的時候<delay8 />就按<colour id="1" /><colour id="65535" />吧！<delay20 />
你可以從裡面<delay8 />選一個喜歡的來用！<pageBreak /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="3" />，我會請島上的其他人<delay20 />
也教你怎麼使用表情！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你就儘管用吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="Sneezing" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">我說<tag a="110" b="3" />啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><tag a="10" b="12" /><anim id="Sneezing" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 /><10_10 /><size value="150" />哈啾！！！<size value="100" /><10_9 /><pageBreak /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嘿嘿，<delay20 />好像有人
正在談論我啊～？<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這種時候，你也<tag a="110" b="0" />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哈<tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="Sneezing" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 /><10_10 />哈啾！！<10_9 /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你也可以<delay8 />用用看「打噴嚏」喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="Frantic" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />喂，快聽我說！<delay frames="30" />
從剛剛開始，<delay8 />我背後就一直有沙沙聲耶！<delay frames="30" />
這到底是怎麼回事啊！？<pageBreak /><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />什麼！？<delay8 />你說我身上黏了一張紙？<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />什麼嘛～原來是這樣啊！<10_4 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊，<delay8 /><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我可沒被嚇到喔！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我只是想要教你
「緊張」的表情要怎麼做而已！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />我、我說的是真的啦──！！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="Surprised" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好──！<delay20 />
我今天<delay8 />要教你<delay8 />
一個新的表情喔！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />「嚇一跳！」<delay8 />這種的怎麼樣～？<delay20 />
就像這樣……<anim id="Surprised" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你可以在盡情健身結束以後，<delay20 />
但肌肉<delay8 />卻不怎麼痠痛的時候用喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="Cheering" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="10" b="12" /><anim id="Cheering" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 /><size value="150" />你有在努力健身嗎──！？<size value="100" /><delay frames="30" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嘿嘿，<delay20 />大聲幫別人加油<delay20 />還滿舒暢的喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你也試著「加油～！」，<delay20 />
幫別人加油吧！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就像<delay8 />這種感覺<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><tag a="10" b="12" /><anim id="Cheering" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 /><size value="150" />肌肉萬歲！<size value="100" /><delay frames="30" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="Dance" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我問你喔，<delay8 />說到英雄的話，<delay8 />
通常都會聯想到勝利姿勢對吧──！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我剛才想到了一個很棒的姿勢！<delay20 />
今天就特別<delay8 />讓你看看吧──！<pageBreak /><anim id="Dance" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="40" /><tag a="110" b="10" /><delay8 />在此登場！！<10_4 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />學會「轉轉～將！」後，<delay20 />就算突然有人<delay8 />
要找你去當英雄，也沒有問題啦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>